(221132, 7386, 220926, 'AK47', 162, '', 1318939352, 'Thanks Chief for the excellent pictorial comparison and taking the time out to reply the question in question!\n\nNice sum up above and very nicely drawn up pro''s/con''s, and I cannot but agree only on most of your observations. \n\nI basically disagree, however, on the carry of Rami with the extended mag and bringing it at par for comparison with the 16 shots Duty.\n \nRami''s original charm is with the 10 shots mag only and that reflects also it''s actual "personality" the most.\n\nIf I was asked to choose a Rami 14 shots vs Duty 16 shots, my choice would be quite naturally in favor of the Duty, with all other goodies added of a compact. Rami''s upgrade being kind of [I]artificial[/I] only.\n\nYet, for the [B]back up[/B], Rami is the way to go sub 350K''s and 10 rounds suffice the purpose.\n\n\nRegards.', 1, 1, '119.154.149.195', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
