(222061, 7293, 221977, 'Rotorcrafts', 348, '', 1319457373, '[QUOTE=AirSoft;221977]Airsoft guns shoot plastic BBs. They are not designed to penetrate into a person or an animal. It might cause internal injuries which would ultimately kill the bird after a prolonged period of suffering, but it won''t have enough energy to kill it cleanly.\n\nIt is possible to kill a small bird if you hit it and continue shooting it while it is down until you walk up to it and shoot it at point-blank range. You''ll be pummeling it to death with small plastic balls rather than shooting it dead.\n\nIf you want a gun for bird hunting, a pellet rifle is a much better choice.[/QUOTE]\n\nLols, I cant stop thinking about the poor Imaginary bird... :D', 1, 1, '39.41.191.18', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
