(222954, 7465, 222952, 'Crazy Shooter', 2880, '', 1319767767, '[QUOTE=Hamid;222952]Nothing is wrong with the gun or your shooting. Please answer some questions.\n\nDo you see part of the shotgun rib when you mount the gun or just the bead?\nAre you sure you don''t lift your head off the stock when you fire?\n\n\nPS: Try to check your gun''s point of impact on a chart paper and post the result here.[/QUOTE]\n\n\nI see part of the short gun rib and I dnt lift my head off stock when I fire and I have already fired at charts at 20 to 25 meters I am just fine with that but cant take a flying shot like I used to with my SxS and single barrel shotguns.\n\nFor doves, IC or even Cylinder works fine with #7 or #6. Choke selection is more of a personal/practical matter. I use modified for everything and its works fine for me.', 1, 1, '110.39.134.78', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
